<li id="cite_note-114"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-114">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">See for example Michalski, xi. Here Michalski refers to this rejection of religious imagery within Calvinism as "iconophobia". See also Gäbler, 72, 76–77 and Potter, 130–31 regarding the religious disputations in Zürich (1523) concerning (among other things) the removal of statues of saints and other icons. Participants included <a href="Leo_Jud" title="Leo Jud">Leo Jud</a> and <a href="Huldrych_Zwingli" title="Huldrych Zwingli">Huldrych Zwingli</a>.</span></li>
